title: to delete a network connection from KDE's Network Manager
pid: c81ed244-5cab-4ef7-86bf-11c351488d78
body: |2-
  Run
    nmcli connection delete <connection name>
  where <connection name> is what appears in the network manager GUI.
  The name should be in parentheses, and capitalization matters.
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
